is debut for Covilh\u00e3 in a league match against [[C.F. Uni\u00e3o|Uni\u00e3o da Madeira]] where he coming on as a substitute for [[Hugo Moreira (footballer, born 1982)|Hugo Moreira]] in the 86th minute.<ref>{{cite web|title=Sporting Covilh\u00e3 vs. Uni\u00e3o Madeira  1 - 3|url=https://int.soccerway.com/matches/2012/11/28/portugal/liga-de-honra/sc-covilha/cf-uniao-madeira/1317169/ |publisher=soccerway|accessdate=21 May 2013}}</ref> He left Covilh\u00e3 at the end of 2012/13 league season.\n\nIn February 2014, Li transferred to [[China League One]] side [[Chengdu Tiancheng]].<ref>[http://sports.sina.com.cn/b/2014-02-27/16197043638.shtml \u6210\u90fd\u5929\u8bda\u7b7e\u7ea6\u201c\u9a6c\u660e\u5b87\u7b2c\u4e8c\u201d \u5929\u624d\u5c0f\u5c06\u66fe\u62d2\u7533\u82b1] at sports.qq.com 2014-02-27 Retrieved 2014-02-27</ref> He made his debut for Chengdu on 27 July 2014 in a 2\u20131 home defeat against [[Qingdao Huanghai F.C.|Qingdao Hainiu]], coming on as a substitute for [[Gao Xiang (footballer)|Gao Xiang]] in the 82nd minute.<ref>[http://sports.sina.com.cn/b/2014-07-27/22267268937.shtml \u4e2d\u7532-\u66f2\u6ce2\u7834\u95e8\u5bfc\u6f14\u9006\u8f6c \u6210\u90fd1-2\u6d77\u725b\u674e\u7ae0\u6d19\u906d\u4e24\u8fde\u8d25] at sports.sina.com 2014-07-27 Retrieved 2016-11-04</ref> At Chengdu he would play in [[Midfielder|midfield]] and [[Defender (association football)|defence]], however none of these changes would help in seeing the club avoid relegation at the end of the season, which saw Li become an unattached player in 2015 after Chengdu dissolved due to the downgrade.<ref>[http://sports.sohu.com/20141102/n405693595.shtml 2014\u8d5b\u5b63\u4e2d\u7532\u7b2c30\u8f6e\u540e\u79ef\u5206\u699c] at sports.sohu.com 2014-11-02 Retrieved 2018-10-24</ref>\n\nLi joined [[China Super League]] side [[Chongqing Lifan]] in the 2016 season.<ref>[http://sports.163.com/16/0225/01/BGKQF52R00051C89.html \u529b\u5e06\u786e\u5b9a30\u4eba\u5927\u540d\u5355] at sports.163.com 2016-02-25 Retrie