 Aquino III]]}}\n{{s-break}}\n{{s-bef|before=[[Recep Tayyip Erdo\u011fan]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=Chairperson of the [[G20|Group of 20]]|years=2016}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[Angela Merkel]]}}\n{{s-break}}\n{{s-mil}}\n{{s-bef|before=[[Zhu De]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[People's Liberation Army|Commander-in-Chief of the People's Liberation Army]]|years=2016\u2013present}}\n{{s-inc}}\n{{s-break}}\n{{s-aca}}\n{{s-bef|before=[[Zeng Qinghong]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[Central Party School of the Communist Party of China|President of the Central Party School]]|years=2007\u20132013}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[Liu Yunshan]]}}\n{{s-break}}\n{{s-prec}}\n{{s-break}}\n{{s-new|first}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[Orders of precedence in the People's Republic of China|Rank of the Communist Party of China]]<br />{{small|18th [[Politburo Standing Committee of the Communist Party of China|Politburo Standing Committee]]}}}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[Li Keqiang]]|as=[[Premier of the State Council]]}}\n{{s-end}}|titlestyle=background: #CC0000; color:gold;}}{{Navboxes|list1={{Navboxes\n|title=Party and State Positions held\n|list1=\n{{Paramount leaders of the People's Republic of China}}\n{{CCPHeads}}\n{{19th Politburo of the Communist Party of China}}\n{{18th Politburo of the Communist Party of China}}\n{{17th Politburo of the Communist Party of China}}\n{{Presidents of the People's Republic of China}}\n{{CMC Chairman}}\n{{CPC Secretariat}}\n{{Vice Presidents of the People's Republic of China}}\n}}\n{{Navboxes\n|title = Regional offices held\n|list1 =\n{{Shanghai leaders}}\n{{Zhejiang leaders}}\n{{Fujian leaders}}\n}}\n{{Navboxes\n|title = International\n|list1 =\n{{Currentcommunistrulers}}\n{{List of Current Heads of State of G20}}\n{{Current G20 Leaders}}\n{{BRICS}}\n{{Current APEC Leaders}}\n{{Current SCO Leaders}}\n}}\n|titlestyle=background: #CC0000; color:gold;}}\n{{Portal bar|China|Biography|Politics}}\n{{Subject bar|commons=y|n=y|n-search=Category:Xi Jinping|wikt=y|wikt-search=Category:en:Xi Jinping|q=y|s=y|s-search=Author:Xi Jinping|d=y|d-search=Q15031}}{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Xi, Jinping}}\n[[Category:Xi Jinping| ]]\n[[Category:Xi Jinping family| ]]\n[[Category:1953 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:20th-century Chinese politicians]]\n[[Category:21st-century Chinese politicians]]\n[[Category:Chinese nationalists]]\n[[Category:Philosophers from Beijing]]\n[[Category:Communist rulers]]\n[[Category:Communist Party of China politicians from Beijing]]\n[[Category:General Secretaries and Chairmen of the Communist Party of China]]\n[[Category:Governors of Fujian]]\n[[Category:Governors of Zhejiang]]\n[[Category:Members of the 17th Politburo Standing Committee of the Communist Party of China]]\n[[Category:Members of the 18th Politburo Standing Committee of the Communist Party of China]]\n[[Category:Members of the 19th Politburo Standing Committee of the Communist Party of China]]\n[[Category:People's Republic of China politicians from Beijing]]\n[[Category:Presidents of the People's Republic of China]]\n[[Category:Recipients of the Nishan-e-Pakistan]]\n[[Category:Recipients of the Olympic Order]]\n[[Category:Recipients of the Order of Abdulaziz al Saud]]\n[[Category:Recipients of the Order of Jos\u00e9 Marti]]\n[[Category:Recipients of the Order of St. Andrew]]\n[[Category:Recipients of the Order of the Liberator]]\n[[Category:Recipients of the Order of the Republic (Serbia)]]\n[[Category:Chinese male writers]]\n[[Category:Sent-down youths]]\n[[Category:Tsinghua University alumni]]\n[[Category:Vice Presidents of the People's Republic of China]]\n[[Category:People's Republic of China philosophers]]\n[[Category:Victims of the Cultural Revolution]]\n[[Category:Chinese expatriates in the United States]]\n[[Category:Communist writers]]\n[[Category:Chinese Marxists]]\n", "text_old": "{{pp-blp|small=yes}}\n{{pp-move-indef|small=yes}}\n{{short description|General Secretary of the Communist Party of China and paramount leader of China}}\n\n{{Use dmy dates|date=October 2019}}\n{{u